CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper January 9, 1960, pg. 11, reads: "Seneca Presents - The Goodwin and O'Hara operetta, 'The Christmas Thieves,' was presented by the Seneca Junior High recently in the school's auditorium. Above are members of the cast. Left to rights: Braden Walter, Laurel Gordon, Adrienne Sproul, Richard Whittaker, Judy Busken, Jean Bruno and Victoria Rizzo. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Seneca Junior High School students and cast of "The Christmas Thieves," from left: Braden Walter, Laurel Gordon, Adrienne Sproul, Richard Whittaker, Judy Busken, Jean Bruno and Victoria Rizzo posed in classroom
